{"word":"G4724 - στέλλω - stéllō - stel'-lo - Avoid","slug":"G4724","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>stéllō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>stel'-lo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Avoid"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C9; - stello&#x0304;</b> - <i>stel'-lo</i><p/>Probably strengthened from the base of <a href=\"#/G2476\">G2476</a>; properly to <i>set</i> fast (&ldquo;stall&rdquo;), that is, (figuratively) to <i>repress</i> (reflexively <i>abstain</i> from associating with): - avoid, withdraw self."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1291\">G1291</a>, <a href=\"#/G1293\">G1293</a>, <a href=\"#/G1989\">G1989</a>, <a href=\"#/G1992\">G1992</a>, <a href=\"#/G2687\">G2687</a>, <a href=\"#/G2689\">G2689</a>, <a href=\"#/G4958\">G4958</a>, <a href=\"#/G5288\">G5288</a>, <a href=\"#/G5289\">G5289</a>"}]}